episodes.title: Ant Hill Gang/Blackburn
episodes.description: Get ready folks. In this episode, we talk about the Ant Hill Gang and the Blackburn cult. We discuss the history, beliefs, and experiences that happened in these cults. Enjoy!

episodes.title: Children of God/Gloriavale
episodes.description: Welcome to "It's Cult O'Clock," the podcast that delves into the intriguing and often disturbing world of cults. In this series, we explore the histories, beliefs, and experiences of various cults, shining a light on the lesser-known aspects of their existence. In this episode, we uncover the untold stories of two notorious cults – the Children of God and the Gloriavale Community.
